  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1 - \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Shooting in Colombo Kotanjenai - One killed",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 51-year-old man was shot dead by two unidentified men on a motorcycle last night at Vivekananda Road, Kotanchen, Colombo.",
        "Police said that two unidentified men on a motorcycle opened fire on Kotanchenai Vivekananda Road.",
        "Meanwhile, both the killers have escaped and the Coastal Police is conducting further investigations to arrest them."
      ],
